{"tid":799117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女老師上妝變性感野貓　高調睡學生被控性侵","createTime":"2018-08-29T21:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T21:36:39.000Z","uid":59743,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d52d7f1c14fe03fe87f5a2fa8245b93deb3a42f8","tid":799117,"uid":59743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T21:28:44.000Z","msg":"快點.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180829/640_95108f48d75e3b366bee5d96fea7f5f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180829%2F640_95108f48d75e3b366bee5d96fea7f5f9.jpg&h=384aff2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國奧克拉荷馬州一名29歲高中女老師史瑪特(Haylie Smart)，涉嫌從去年秋天到今年5月高調勾引一名男學生，近日被控二級性侵罪。<br />\n<br />\n據美國《News ON6》網站報導，史瑪特在歐羅加高中(Oologah High School)擔任英文老師，更在班上看上一名17歲鮮肉學生，兩人之後進一步交往，更多次互到彼此家中做愛，也曾在教室裡做愛。不僅如此，兩人更高調地在眾多學生面前大方親熱示愛，兩人的戀情也因此被傳開。最後史瑪特遭到校方調查並停職，而史瑪特也辭職。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，史瑪特在與該名男學生交往期間，男學生在去年12月也從未成年蛻變為18歲成年男子，但據奧克拉荷馬州規定，老師睡學生依舊是違法行為。史瑪特在本月初被逮捕，並被控二級性侵罪，她在上周五被以25000美元(約新台幣75萬元)交保。史瑪特也在自家的推特上表示，自己已經離開教職工作，目前正朝向專業小說家之路邁進。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快點...放佢入監獄唔好比佢出黎害學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180829/640_c048e9ec527d8adc5dae46dd2d473dcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180829%2F640_c048e9ec527d8adc5dae46dd2d4